<c.bg_transparent>It's a hearing, not a trial.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:32:49.217 --> 00:32:50.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She has no choice.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:33:00.603 --> 00:33:01.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:33:03.481 --> 00:33:05.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo's on subspace.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:33:05.191 --> 00:33:06.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's urgent.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:33:10.905 --> 00:33:12.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I've made some progress.</i></c.bg_transparent>

541
00:33:12.490 --> 00:33:13.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:33:14.075 --> 00:33:15.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Not good.</i></c.bg_transparent>

543
00:33:15.827 --> 00:33:18.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Since the transmission</i></c.bg_transparent>
