00:33:22.375 --> 00:33:24.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>from headquarters during that period.</i></c.bg_transparent>

547
00:33:24.585 --> 00:33:27.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I even found Curzon Dax's records.</i></c.bg_transparent>

548
00:33:27.463 --> 00:33:30.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't tell me Curzon</c.bg_transparent>
