549
00:33:30.842 --> 00:33:32.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>No, nothing like that,</i></c.bg_transparent>

550
00:33:32.385 --> 00:33:35.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>but the log does show</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>a number of conversations</i></c.bg_transparent>

551
00:33:35.179 --> 00:33:38.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>between Dax's office</i></c.bg_transparent>
