552
00:33:38.641 --> 00:33:39.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They were close friends.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:33:40.059 --> 00:33:44.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>A number of the conversations took place</i></c.bg_transparent>
