554
00:33:47.066 --> 00:33:49.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-The wife.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-The wife.</i></c.bg_transparent>

555
00:33:52.572 --> 00:33:55.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon Dax and Enina Tandro.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:33:56.951 --> 00:33:58.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Maybe it was innocent.</i></c.bg_transparent>

557
00:33:58.494 --> 00:34:00.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Maybe he was just providing</i></c.bg_transparent>
