558
00:34:01.039 --> 00:34:02.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>during tough times.</i></c.bg_transparent>

559
00:34:02.915 --> 00:34:05.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Or maybe they were taking advantage</i></c.bg_transparent>

560
00:34:05.293 --> 00:34:07.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
