00:34:25.229 --> 00:34:26.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The conversations were just the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:34:27.065 --> 00:34:28.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've also found records of gifts,</c.bg_transparent>

