568
00:34:36.157 --> 00:34:37.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If there's more to this</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than meets the eye,</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:34:37.909 --> 00:34:39.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
