571
00:34:46.626 --> 00:34:49.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My husband was not the hero in life</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:34:49.420 --> 00:34:51.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
