578
00:35:04.644 --> 00:35:05.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you don't.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:35:05.812 --> 00:35:10.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, because I knew the man</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before he became a legend.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:35:10.233 --> 00:35:12.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I also know my place in history.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:35:12.777 --> 00:35:16.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My place is to carry on bravely,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>never to remarry,</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:35:16.239 --> 00:35:19.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to represent my husband at the banquets</c.bg_transparent>
