583
00:35:19.575 --> 00:35:22.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But never, never to talk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about who he really was.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:35:23.746 --> 00:35:26.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because nobody wants to hear that.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:35:27.625 --> 00:35:29.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They may have to hear it now.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:35:31.295 --> 00:35:35.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No matter what is said,</c.bg_transparent>
