587
00:35:38.803 --> 00:35:43.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For he was and always will be</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:35:44.392 --> 00:35:47.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
