589
00:35:52.483 --> 00:35:56.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But perhaps it's time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for my place in history to change.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:36:04.328 --> 00:36:06.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been protecting her reputation.</c.bg_transparent>

