598
00:36:37.403 --> 00:36:39.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My God, Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:36:39.113 --> 00:36:41.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
