601
00:36:44.702 --> 00:36:47.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then what is it that's holding you back?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Help me.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:36:49.332 --> 00:36:50.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:36:50.458 --> 00:36:52.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Damn it, if you were still a man...</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:36:54.170 --> 00:36:55.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( bangs wall )</c.bg_transparent>

605
