610
00:37:14.232 --> 00:37:17.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:37:18.819 --> 00:37:22.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you knocked me down with a right cross</c.bg_transparent>
