00:37:45.596 --> 00:37:48.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>because I don't know any more arguments.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:37:50.393 --> 00:37:52.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then allow it to happen.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:37:52.687 --> 00:37:56.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is my obligation to protect the lives</c.bg_transparent>
