630
00:38:32.893 --> 00:38:37.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can tell you... that he did love her</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:38:38.274 --> 00:38:39.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
