632
00:38:40.776 --> 00:38:42.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enough to kill her husband?</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:38:44.780 --> 00:38:46.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you are questioning?</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:38:47.408 --> 00:38:49.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What else can I do?</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:38:51.078 --> 00:38:53.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:38:53.456 --> 00:38:55.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing at all.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:39:11.390 --> 00:39:15.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant Dax, you are either</c.bg_transparent>
