639
00:39:19.857 --> 00:39:22.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At first,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I wondered which of those you were.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:39:22.777 --> 00:39:27.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, I am bothered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by the likelihood that you may be both.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:39:30.743 --> 00:39:32.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's finish this, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:39:34.288 --> 00:39:39.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At what age did the host, Jadzia</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>first want to be joined as a Trill?</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:39:39.335 --> 00:39:42.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted it since I was a child.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I worked very hard for it.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:39:42.630 --> 00:39:45.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The competition to become</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a Trill is very strong, then,</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:39:45.758 --> 00:39:47.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>among potential hosts?</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:39:47.468 --> 00:39:49.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes. It's considered a great honor.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:39:49.845 --> 00:39:52.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did the young Jadzia finally</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>become a host candidate?</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:39:53.015 --> 00:39:57.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>By winning scholarships,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>competing against other young people.</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:39:57.186 --> 00:39:58.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're tested in countless ways.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:39:58.938 --> 00:40:00.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Including psychological tests</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:40:00.481 --> 00:40:02.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to determine strength of character</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the prospective host.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:40:02.691 --> 00:40:03.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that true?</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:40:04.360 --> 00:40:05.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:40:05.611 --> 00:40:10.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the young Jadzia excelled in those</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tests of academics and character--</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:40:10.783 --> 00:40:12.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of psychological stability.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:40:13.619 --> 00:40:14.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:40:15.871 --> 00:40:20.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you can remember other things,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>remember that as well.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:40:22.837 --> 00:40:25.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What academic degrees do you hold,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant?</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:40:26.841 --> 00:40:32.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hold Premier Distinctions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in exobiology, zoology,</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:40:32.388 --> 00:40:35.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>astrophysics, and exoarchaeology.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:40:35.808 --> 00:40:39.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How many of those degrees did you earn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before being joined with the symbiont Dax?</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:40:40.855 --> 00:40:42.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of them.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:40:42.440 --> 00:40:44.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of them.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:40:45.443 --> 00:40:46.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:40:46.986 --> 00:40:47.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alone.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:40:50.614 --> 00:40:53.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This brilliant and independent</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>young woman</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:40:53.993 --> 00:40:57.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>has done nothing in her life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but contribute to her society.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:40:57.872 --> 00:41:01.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Arbiter, how can anyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>justify trying her for a crime</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:41:01.542 --> 00:41:05.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>allegedly committed by another entity</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before she was even born?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:41:08.424 --> 00:41:10.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This will only take a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:41:11.886 --> 00:41:13.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant...</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:41:13.596 --> 00:41:15.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as a Trill candidate,</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:41:15.556 --> 00:41:18.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>did Jadzia fully understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the responsibilities</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:41:18.392 --> 00:41:20.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to be assumed upon becoming a Trill,</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:41:20.478 --> 00:41:22.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and did you willingly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>accept those responsibilities</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:41:23.022 --> 00:41:25.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and whatever consequences</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they might entail?</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:41:26.358 --> 00:41:27.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:41:27.651 --> 00:41:30.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And would that not obviously</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>include the consequences</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:41:30.404 --> 00:41:33.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of criminal acts committed by Curzon Dax?</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:41:33.199 --> 00:41:34.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opening )</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:41:44.960 --> 00:41:46.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I speak?</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:41:46.587 --> 00:41:48.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you are?</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:41:49.340 --> 00:41:51.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am Enina Tandro,</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:41:51.425 --> 00:41:54.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>widow of General Ardelon Tandro.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:41:54.887 --> 00:41:56.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This hearing is unnecessary.</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:41:56.722 --> 00:41:58.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The accusations are erroneous.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:41:58.641 --> 00:42:00.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mother, what are you talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:42:02.186 --> 00:42:03.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Arbiter,</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:42:03.646 --> 00:42:06.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon Dax is accused</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:42:06.482 --> 00:42:10.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of sending a transmission to the enemy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that betrayed my husband.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:42:12.571 --> 00:42:15.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I know where Curzon was</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:42:15.324 --> 00:42:18.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>at the exact time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that transmission was sent.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:42:22.122 --> 00:42:25.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was... in my bed.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:42:45.354 --> 00:42:46.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Tandro,</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:42:46.855 --> 00:42:50.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you will want to reexamine</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your extradition request.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:42:51.819 --> 00:42:53.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Until then,</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:42:53.153 --> 00:42:56.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>this hearing is adjourned.</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:43:08.836 --> 00:43:12.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was kind of you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to try and protect me...</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:43:13.257 --> 00:43:15.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>someone you'd never even met.</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:43:15.801 --> 00:43:18.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's much of Curzon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's still a part of me,</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:43:18.887 --> 00:43:22.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that still remembers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you had together.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:43:22.474 --> 00:43:26.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it was Curzon Dax</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who swore himself to silence</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:43:26.270 --> 00:43:30.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to preserve the memory</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of General Tandro, not Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:43:30.858 --> 00:43:34.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I felt it was important</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to keep that promise.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:43:34.528 --> 00:43:38.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The General's memory</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is cherished by your people.</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:43:38.824 --> 00:43:41.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And it will continue to be.</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:43:42.328 --> 00:43:46.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, no one will ever know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that he was the one who tried to betray us</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:43:46.874 --> 00:43:50.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and that the rebels</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>killed him for the favor.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:43:53.130 --> 00:43:57.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As for you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there is one favor I would ask.</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:43:59.053 --> 00:44:01.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:44:02.097 --> 00:44:04.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Live, Jadzia Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:44:13.942 --> 00:44:17.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Live a long, fresh, and wonderful life.</c.bg_transparent>

